{"questionId":"13673","questionHtml":"<p>Find the coordinates of the points on the curve&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{y^3} + 3x{y^2} - {x^3} = 27\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>y</mi>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>y</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>27</mn>\n</math></span> at which <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{{\\text{d}}y}}{{{\\text{d}}x}} = 0\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>d</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mi>y</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>d</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p style=\"color:#999;font-size:90%;font-style:italic;\">* This question is from an exam for a previous syllabus, and may contain minor differences in marking or structure.</p><p>attempt at implicit differentiation&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"3{y^2}\\frac{{{\\text{d}}y}}{{{\\text{d}}x}} + 3{y^2} + 6xy\\frac{{{\\text{d}}y}}{{{\\text{d}}x}} - 3{x^2} = 0\">\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>y</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>d</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mi>y</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>d</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>y</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>6</mn>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mi>y</mi>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>d</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mi>y</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>d</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em><em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>A1</strong></em> for the second &amp; third terms, <em><strong>A1</strong></em> for the first term, fourth term &amp; RHS equal to zero.</p>\n<p>substitution of&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{{\\text{d}}y}}{{{\\text{d}}x}} = 0\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>d</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mi>y</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>d</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"3{y^2} - 3{x^2} = 0\">\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>y</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" \\Rightarrow y =&nbsp; \\pm x\">\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>y</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>±</mo>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>substitute either variable into original equation&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"y = x \\Rightarrow {x^3} = 9 \\Rightarrow x = \\sqrt[3]{9}\">\n  <mi>y</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>9</mn>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mroot>\n    <mn>9</mn>\n    <mn>3</mn>\n  </mroot>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;(or&nbsp; <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{y^3} =&nbsp; 9&nbsp;\\Rightarrow y = \\sqrt[3]{9}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>y</mi>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>9</mn>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>y</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mroot>\n    <mn>9</mn>\n    <mn>3</mn>\n  </mroot>\n</math></span>)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"y =&nbsp; - x \\Rightarrow {x^3} = 27 \\Rightarrow x = 3\">\n  <mi>y</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>27</mn>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;(or&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{y^3} =&nbsp; - 27 \\Rightarrow y =&nbsp; - 3\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>y</mi>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>27</mn>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>y</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n</math></span>)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\sqrt[3]{9}{\\text{,}}\\,\\,\\sqrt[3]{9}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mroot>\n        <mn>9</mn>\n        <mn>3</mn>\n      </mroot>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>,</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mroot>\n        <mn>9</mn>\n        <mn>3</mn>\n      </mroot>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> , (3,&nbsp;−3)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[9 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"13673","referenceCode":"19M.1.AHL.TZ1.H_7","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Find the coordinates of the points on the curve y 3 + 3 x y 2 − x 3 = 27 at which d y d x = 0 .","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"H_7","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 9]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 5 —Calculus","Topic 5 —Calculus","SL 5.3—Differentiating polynomials, n E Z","Topic 5 —Calculus","AHL 5.14—Implicit functions, related rates, optimisation"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}